name: Simply Goblin
description:
Usenase doesn't speak to Podase
neither of the two wish to
harken the yaks of another
Yet otherwordly prattle
persists betwix the two
For sure it must Bezobzir
whose whines escape
into the uncordial night,
into uncordial ears.
Nemilost wishes for it to end
and so he schemes with Ratomir
and ghoulish plans to come to a forge
"Gorge the eyes out of your kindered
my friends Potrbuh and Požudar,
of Daruvar perhaps
for the knave needen't those he has
already purblinded by crooked Pretvara."
All know nothing but wickedness and treachery
Falsity and snitching being
to them as natural as the warts
potruding upon their clammy skin”
Text by Ana Strazicic @purikulo
Artists: Tea Strazicic, Christian Thomsen (Fjorsk), Finley Stewart
Info:
“Simply Goblin” - Group show by Tea Strazicic, Christian Thomsen (Fjorsk) and Finley
Stewart at Erratum Gallery, Berlin, On June 30th, 2021
